#MEM id=rate-limiting source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/raj/skills/custom/rate-limiting/SKILL.md savings=5%
M||tx|---
M||name|rate-limiting
M||desc|Rate limiting implementation for yv using vc Edge mw. Covers per-rt limits, sliding window pattern, 429 rp format, and sb-based fallback. No Upstash — not in yv's stack.
M||vers|1.0.0
M||tx|---
M|Purp|tx|w/o rate limiting, yv's AI rt (`/ap/team-chat`, `/ap/*-ag`) can be exhausted by a single client making rapid requests — burning Anthropic ap credits and degrading rp qual for all us. This skill defines what rj implements and how.
M|Purp|tx|---
M|Per-|tx|\| rt category \| Limit \| Window \|
M|Per-|tx|\|---------------\|-------\|--------\|
M|Per-|tx|\| AI rt (`/ap/team-chat`, `/ap/*-ag`, `/ap/creative-engine`) \| 20 req/min \| per IP \|
M|Per-|tx|\| Data rt (`/ap/an`, `/ap/cr`, `/ap/sl`) \| 60 req/min \| per IP \|
M|Per-|tx|\| Auth rt \| 10 req/min \| per IP \|
M|Per-|tx|\| Cron rt \| 1 req/min \| enforced by vc schedule, not mw \|
M|Per-|tx|---
M|Requ|tx|```ts
M|Requ|tx|return NextResponse.json(
M|Requ|er|'Rate limit exceeded. Please wait before retrying.' },
M|Requ|tx|{
M|Requ|stat|429,
M|Requ|head|{
M|Requ|'Ret|'60',
M|Requ|'X-R|String(limit),
M|Requ|'X-R|'0',
M|Requ|'X-R|String(Math.ceil(Date.now() / 1000) + 60)
M|Requ|tx|}
M|Requ|tx|}
M|Requ|tx|)
M|Requ|tx|```
M|Requ|tx|Never return `200` or `500` for a rate limit. Always `429` w/ `Retry-After`.
